data.title: TECO Energy
data.text:
As of the July 1, 2016, acquisition of TECO Energy, Inc. by Emera Inc., TECO Energy is no longer a publicly traded company.

For questions regarding uncashed TECO Energy, Inc. stock certificates and/or dividends, please contact our pay agent, American Stock Transfer (AST) 1-877-361-7963.
